    - This package is now maintained by the Debian Games Team.
    - Add Eshat Cakar and myself to Uploaders.
  * Remove useless build-deps on xlibmesa-gl-dev and xutils (Closes: #579040).
  * Add support for amd64 (Closes: #402104)
